trans-unit.source: Retrieves the Map object associated with this RowSet object, which specifies the custom mapping of SQL user-defined types, if any.
Retrieves the Map object associated with this RowSet object, which specifies the custom mapping of SQL user-defined types, if any. The default is for the type map to be empty.
Retrieves the SQLException for this ConnectionEvent object.
Retrieves the SQLException for this ConnectionEvent object. May be null.
Retrieves the Statement object that produced this ResultSet object.
Retrieves the Statement object that produced this ResultSet object. If the result set was generated some other way, such as by a DatabaseMetaData method, this method may return null.
Retrieves the String that this database uses as the separator between a catalog and table name.
Retrieves the SyncProvider implementation for this CachedRowSet object.

For example, a rowset may need to get a handle on the rowset reader (RowSetReader object) from the SyncProvider to allow the rowset to be populated.

Retrieves the altName field of this exception.

Retrieves the altName field of this exception. This is the name of the resolved object, relative to the context altNameCtx. It will be used during a subsequent call to the javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance method.
trans-unit.target: 检索此异常的 altName 字段。这是相对于上下文 altNameCtx 的已解析对象的名称。在后续调用 javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance 方法期间将使用它。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the altNameCtx field of this exception.

Retrieves the altNameCtx field of this exception. This is the context relative to which altName is named. It will be used during a subsequent call to the javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance method.
trans-unit.target: 检索此异常的 altNameCtx 字段。这是相对于 altName 命名的上下文。在后续调用 javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance 方法期间将使用它。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP control.

Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP control. The result is the raw BER bytes including the tag and length of the control's value. It does not include the controls OID or criticality. Null is returned if the value is absent.
trans-unit.target: 检索LDAP控件的ASN.1 BER编码值。结果是原始误码率字节,包括标签和控件值的长度。它不包括控件的OID或关键性。如果没有值,则返回空值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP extended operation request.

Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP extended operation request. Null is returned if the value is absent. The result is the raw BER bytes including the tag and length of the request value. It does not include the request OID. This method is called by the service provider to get the bits to put into the extended operation to be sent to the LDAP server.
trans-unit.target: 检索LDAP扩展操作请求的ASN.1 BER编码值。如果没有该值,则返回空值。结果是原始的BER字节,包括请求值的标签和长度,不包括请求OID。它不包括请求OID。这个方法被服务提供者调用,以获得要放到要发送给LDAP服务器的扩展操作中的位。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP extended operation response.

Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP extended operation response. Null is returned if the value is absent from the response sent by the LDAP server. The result is the raw BER bytes including the tag and length of the response value. It does not include the response OID.
trans-unit.target: 检索LDAP扩展操作响应的ASN.1 BER编码值。如果LDAP服务器发送的响应中没有这个值,则返回空值。结果是原始的BER字节,包括标签和响应值的长度。它不包括响应OID。

Retrieves the DBMS-specific type name for values stored in the designated column.

trans-unit.target: 检索解析成功的对象。

Retrieves the SQL query that is the command for this RowSet object. The command property contains the query that will be executed to populate this RowSet object.

Retrieves the SQL structured type instance referenced by this Ref object. If the connection's type map has an entry for the structured type, the instance will be custom mapped to the Java class indicated in the type map. Otherwise, the structured type instance will be mapped to a Struct object.

Retrieves the SQL type name of the elements in the array designated by this Array object. If the elements are a built-in type, it returns the database-specific type name of the elements. If the elements are a user-defined type (UDT), this method returns the fully-qualified SQL type name.
Retrieves the SQL type of the elements in this SerialArray object.
Retrieves the SQL type of the elements in this SerialArray object. The int returned is one of the constants in the class java.sql.Types.
Retrieves the SQLState for this SQLException object.

Retrieves the StartTLS request's ASN.1 BER encoded value. Since the request has no defined value, null is always returned.

trans-unit.target: 检索StartTLS请求的对象标识符字符串。

trans-unit.target: 检索StartTLS响应的对象标识符字符串。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the URL for this DBMS.
Retrieves the XML value designated by this SQLXML instance as a java.io.Reader object.

Retrieves the XML value designated by this SQLXML instance as a java.io.Reader object. The format of this stream is defined by org.xml.sax.InputSource, where the characters in the stream represent the unicode code points for XML according to section 2 and appendix B of the XML 1.0 specification. Although an encoding declaration other than unicode may be present, the encoding of the stream is unicode. The behavior of this method is the same as ResultSet.getCharacterStream() when the designated column of the ResultSet has a type java.sql.Types of SQLXML.
Retrieves the XML value designated by this SQLXML instance as a stream.

Retrieves the XML value designated by this SQLXML instance as a stream. The bytes of the input stream are interpreted according to appendix F of the XML 1.0 specification. The behavior of this method is the same as ResultSet.getBinaryStream() when the designated column of the ResultSet has a type java.sql.Types of SQLXML.

Retrieves the attribute value from the ordered list of attribute values. This method returns the value at the ix index of the list of attribute values. If the attribute values are unordered, this method returns the value that happens to be at that index.
trans-unit.target: 从属性值的有序列表中检索属性值。此方法返回属性值列表的 ix 索引处的值。如果属性值是无序的，则此方法返回恰好在该索引处的值。

trans-unit.target: 从属性集中检索给定属性id的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attribute's schema definition.

Retrieves the attribute's schema definition. An attribute's schema definition contains information such as whether the attribute is multivalued or single-valued, the matching rules to use when comparing the attribute's values. The information that you can retrieve from an attribute definition is directory-dependent.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性的模式定义。一个属性的模式定义包含了一些信息,如属性是多值还是单值,比较属性值时要使用的匹配规则。从属性定义中可以检索到的信息是依赖于目录的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attributes associated with an entry.
trans-unit.target: 检索与一个条目相关的属性。

Retrieves the callback function that selects an application protocol value during a SSL/TLS/DTLS handshake. See setHandshakeApplicationProtocolSelector for the function's type parameters.

Retrieves the catalog names available in this database. The results are ordered by catalog name.

Retrieves the change information for this event. The value of the change information is service-specific. For example, it could be an ID that identifies the change in a change log on the server.
trans-unit.target: 检索该事件的变更信息。变更信息的值是与服务相关的。例如,它可以是一个ID,用于标识服务器上变更日志中的变更。

Retrieves the character position at which the specified Clob object searchstr appears in this Clob object. The search begins at position start.

Retrieves the character position at which the specified substring searchstr appears in the SQL CLOB value represented by this Clob object. The search begins at position start.

Retrieves the class name of the object bound to the name of this binding. If a reference or some other indirect information is bound, retrieves the class name of the eventual object that will be returned by Binding.getObject().
trans-unit.target: 检索绑定到此绑定名称的对象的类名称。如果绑定了引用或其他一些间接信息，则检索 Binding.getObject() 返回的最终对象的类名。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the class name of the object bound to the name of this binding. If the class name has been set explicitly, return it. Otherwise, if this binding contains a non-null object, that object's class name is used. Otherwise, null is returned.
trans-unit.target: 检索与该绑定名称绑定的对象的类名。如果类名已被明确设置,则返回它。否则,如果该绑定包含一个非空对象,则使用该对象的类名。否则,将返回null。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the class name of the object to which this reference refers.
trans-unit.target: 检索该引用所指向的对象的类名。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this composite name as an enumeration of strings.
Retrieves the components of this composite name as an enumeration of strings. The effects of updates to this composite name on this enumeration is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的方式检索这个复合名称的组件。对这个复合名称的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this compound name as an enumeration of strings.
Retrieves the components of this compound name as an enumeration of strings. The effects of updates to this compound name on this enumeration is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的形式检索这个复合名称的组件。对这个复合名称的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this name as an enumeration of strings.

Retrieves the components of this name as an enumeration of strings. The effect of updates to this name on this enumeration is undefined. If the name has zero components, an empty (non-null) enumeration is returned. The order of the components returned by the enumeration is same as the order in which the components are numbered as described in the class description.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的形式检索此名称的组件。对这个名字的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。如果这个名字的组件为零,则返回一个空的(非空)枚举。枚举返回的组件顺序与类描述中描述的组件编号顺序相同。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this name as an enumeration of strings. The effect on the enumeration of updates to this name is undefined. If the name has zero components, an empty (non-null) enumeration is returned.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的方式检索这个名字的组件。对这个名字的更新枚举的影响是未定义的。如果这个名字的组件为零,则返回一个空的(非空)枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the concurrency mode of this ResultSet object.
Retrieves the concurrency mode of this ResultSet object. The concurrency used is determined by the Statement object that created the result set.

Retrieves the connection request controls in effect for this context. The controls are owned by the JNDI implementation and are immutable. Neither the array nor the controls may be modified by the caller.
trans-unit.target: 检索此上下文有效的连接请求控件。这些控件由JNDI实现拥有,并且是不可改变的。数组和控件都不能被调用者修改。

Retrieves the constraints for the specified component. The return value is not a copy, but is the actual GridBagConstraints object used by the layout mechanism.

Retrieves the contents of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object in the form of an array in the Java programming language. This version of the method getArray uses the type map associated with the connection for customizations of the type mappings.
Retrieves the contents of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object.

Retrieves the contents of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object. This method uses the specified map for type map customizations unless the base type of the array does not match a user-defined type in map, in which case it uses the standard mapping. This version of the method getArray uses either the given type map or the standard mapping; it never uses the type map associated with the connection.

trans-unit.target: 检索这个URL连接的内容。

Retrieves the contents of this address as an Object. The result is a byte array. Changes to this array will affect this BinaryRefAddr's contents. Programs are recommended against changing this array's contents and to lock the buffer if they need to change it.
trans-unit.target: 以Object的形式检索该地址的内容。结果是一个字节数组。对这个数组的改变将影响这个BinaryRefAddr的内容。建议程序不要更改这个数组的内容,如果需要更改,请锁定缓冲区。

trans-unit.target: 检索该地址的内容。结果是一个字符串。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties and no controls.
Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties and no controls. The referral context is created using env as its environment properties and no controls.
trans-unit.target: 使用环境属性而不使用控件来检索继续该方法的上下文。引用上下文是使用 env 作为其环境属性而没有控件创建的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties.

Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索使用环境属性继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是间接遇到的,例如在搜索枚举中,引用异常都应该提供一个继续操作的上下文。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using request controls and environment properties.

Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using request controls and environment properties. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation. To continue the operation, the client program should re-invoke the method using the same arguments as the original invocation.
trans-unit.target: 使用请求控件和环境属性检索继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是在搜索枚举中间接遇到的,引用异常都应该提供一个可以继续操作的上下文。为了继续操作,客户端程序应该使用与原始调用相同的参数重新调用该方法。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using the context's environment and no controls.

Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using the context's environment and no controls. The referral context is created using the environment properties of the context that threw the ReferralException and no controls.
trans-unit.target: 检索上下文，使用上下文环境在没有控件的情况下继续该方法。引用上下文是使用抛出 ReferralException 且没有控件的上下文的环境属性创建的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method.

Retrieves the context at which to continue the method. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation. The referral context is created using the environment properties of the context that threw the ReferralException.
trans-unit.target: 检索继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是在搜索枚举中间接遇到的,引用异常都应该提供一个继续操作的上下文。引用上下文是使用抛出 ReferralException 的上下文的环境属性创建的。

trans-unit.target: 检索控制的ASN.1 BER编码值,结果包括控制值的BER标签和长度,但不包括控制的对象标识符和临界度设置。结果包括控制值的BER标签和长度,但不包括控制的对象标识符和临界度设置。

trans-unit.source: Return the current location of the processor.

Return the current location of the processor. If the Location is unknown the processor should return an implementation of Location that returns -1 for the location and null for the publicId and systemId. The location information is only valid until next() is called.
Return the current namespace context.
Return the current size/location of the thumb.
Return the current stream to which output from this log is sent.

Return the default locale's orientation.
Return the default size of an empty display area of the combo box using the current renderer and font.
Return the draw layered highlights.
Return the element that must be next.
Return the embedded exception, if any.
Return the entry name for this connection.
Return the entry name for this connection. This method returns null if the JAR file URL corresponding to this connection points to a JAR file and not a JAR file entry.
trans-unit.target: 返回此连接的条目名。如果这个连接对应的JAR文件URL指向一个JAR文件而不是JAR文件条目,那么本方法返回null。

trans-unit.source: Return the first implementation that has the desired features, or null if none is found.
Return the first index argument from the most recent call to setSelectionInterval(), addSelectionInterval() or removeSelectionInterval().

Return the first index argument from the most recent call to setSelectionInterval(), addSelectionInterval() or removeSelectionInterval(). The most recent index0 is considered the "anchor" and the most recent index1 is considered the "lead". Some interfaces display these indices specially, e.g. Windows95 displays the lead index with a dotted yellow outline.
Return the grouping size.
Return the grouping size. Grouping size is the number of digits between grouping separators in the integer portion of a number. For example, in the number "123,456.78", the grouping size is 3.
trans-unit.target: 返回分组大小。分组大小是指一个数字的整数部分的分组分隔符之间的位数。例如,在数字 "123,456.78 "中,分组大小是3。
